Insider Activity


Individual




Walden C. Rhines



Dr. Walden C. Rhines is Independent Director at Qorvo, Inc. and Chairman & Chief Executive Officer at Mentor Graphics Corp. He is on the Board of Directors at Qorvo, Inc., Semiconductor Research Corp., The Oregon Engineering & Technology Industry Council, Classic Wines Auction, Inc., Electronic Design Automation Consortium, and GlobalLogic, Inc.
Dr. Rhines was previously employed as Independent Director by TriQuint Semiconductor, Inc. and Executive Vice President-Semiconductor Group by Texas Instruments, Incorporated. He also served on the board at Cirrus Logic, Inc., Computer & Business Equipment Manufacturers Association, Lewis & Clark College, and SEMATECH, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Michigan, a graduate degree from Stanford University, an MBA from Southern Methodist University, and a doctorate degree from Stanford University.



